## 5. raw#10 honest C3

1. **inclisiran Leqvio 2021** = first hepatic-targeted siRNA + first PCSK9 siRNA — twice-yearly SC paradigm 변화. compliance 향상 + Q-2/Q-4 mAb 대비 유리. quantum-VQE 의 RNA-target 결합 modeling fit.
2. **evolocumab + alirocumab Repatha/Praluent 2015** = first PCSK9 mAb pair — FOURIER + ODYSSEY-OUTCOMES ASCVD risk reduction. statin + ezetimibe 후 add-on standard. quantum-VQE 의 catalytic + prodomain epitope leverage.
3. **evinacumab Evkeeza 2021** = first FDA ANGPTL3 mAb — HoFH ELIPSE-HoFH 47% LDL 감소. LDLR-independent mechanism (HoFH null homozygote 도 효과). quantum-VQE 의 ANGPTL3 binding interface 가 directly fit.
4. **lomitapide Juxtapid 2012** = first FDA MTTP — HoFH 만성 hepatotox + GI 부작용 (REMS). 임상 위치 한정 + apheresis 보조. evinacumab 등장 후 시장 축소.
5. **mipomersen Kynamro 2013→2018W** = first ApoB ASO HoFH — 2018 withdrawn (hepatotox + 효과 한정). ASO paradigm 의 first failure. olezarsen 2024 가 APOC3 ASO 로 paradigm restore.
6. **olezarsen Tryngolza 2024** = first FDA APOC3 ASO FCS (familial chylomicronemia syndrome) — Balance trial. plozasiran siRNA Phase 3 SHASTA-3 가 next.
7. **VERVE-101 first-in-human 2022** = first PCSK9 base editing in vivo (CRISPR adenine deaminase + LNP 간 표적). chronic alternative — once-and-done paradigm 가능성. Phase 1 ongoing 2025.
8. **obicetrapib NewAmsterdam Phase 3 PRESERVE** = first CETP HDL — torcetrapib/dalcetrapib/anacetrapib/evacetrapib 4 failure 후 5번째 도전. CETP HDL paradigm restore 가능성.
9. **Lp(a) elevation cross-pharmacogenomics** = pelacarsen (Ionis) ASO + olpasiran (arc-1, Amgen) + lepodisiran (Lilly) siRNA Phase 3 — Lp(a) 첫 modifiable target paradigm 형성.
10. **wet-lab + clinical RCT 없음** — quantum-only in-silico, FH 임상 의미 한정. K-FH 등록 + cascade screening + 산정특례 framework 와 cross-link 필요.

